::: Ra, the Egyptian diety and ruler of the Egyptian gods, made his way onto 
the battle feild. He wore a headset, with a cobra crowning him. :::

::: Ra ::: Ah, the first battle of this planet. Let us be thankful, for the 
evergiving elements of nature, space, and time for giving us this oppertunity.

::: He silently makes a prayer, and takes out a small pistol ::::

:: Ra :: Now, we battle.

~~~~~~~~~~~~

::: Transanulas runs over to Quickstrike with a Medkit, while Marine opposes 
Darkmouse. :::

:: Marine :: Are you my soldiers?

~~~~~~~~~~~~~

::: Set looked at Hell Beast, and then to Megatron. :::

::: Set ::: My troops are outside as we speak, destroying your fractions.

::: Hell Beast ::: You wont win, my men are relentless. They will prevail and 
i will hold your head in in my hands.

::: Set ::: Stop with the meaningless speaches. I have a batle to control. 
And Megatron...we will have the tech box soon. Then, you will tell us 
everything.

::: Megatron nods and gives a grim look to Hell Beast :::
